<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186322>
    bibo:endPage "12" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "2033" ;
    dc:creator "Fery, Hans; Erman, Ömer Köksal" ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Five new species of the longulus - group of Hydroporus Clairville, 1806 from north-eastern Turkey (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186323>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186326>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186325>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186324> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186323>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Median lobe of aedeagus of: (1) Hydroporus cagrankaya sp. n. (holotype), (2) H. sivrikaya sp. n. (holotype), (3) H. artvinensis sp. n. (holotype), (4) H. toledoi sp. n. (holotype), (5 a, b) H. lundbergi sp. n. (holotype) (the arrow indicates the direction of the \" frontal view \", Fig. 5 b)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186323/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186326>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Distribution of Hydroporus lundbergi sp. n. (1 – 3; see text), H. cagrankaya sp. n. (4), H. sivrikaya sp. n. (5), H. toledoi sp. n. (6), H. artvinensis sp. n. (7), and H. erzurumensis (8 – 14). The map was made by using MS ENCARTA 2000." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186326/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186325>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 12. Hydroporus cagrankaya sp. n.: SEM photos of: (9) parts of venter, (10) left protarsus, (11) left mesotarsus, (12) details of first and second tarsomeres of left protarsus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186325/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186324>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 8. Hydroporus cagrankaya sp. n.: (6) paramere, (7) gonocoxae, (8) gonocoxosternum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186324/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

